definitions.definition: A country in Western Europe and Central Europe . Official name: Swiss Confederation . Capital: Bern ( de facto ) .
examples: Much of Switzerland is located in the Alps .

main_definition: A country in Western Europe and Central Europe . Official name: Swiss Confederation . Capital: Bern ( de facto ) .

definitions.definition: A neutral party in a dispute ; one who does not take sides .
examples: I’m not getting involved in this argument. I’m Switzerland .

main_definition: ( figurative ) A neutral party in a dispute ; one who does not take sides .
